 *           |VM|VM|  |------+------->|  Proxy  |<----------+------|            |
 *           +--+--+--+      |        |         |           |      |            |
 *                           |        |         |           |      +------------+
 *           +--------+      |        +---------+           |      |Inspector   |
 *           | Device |------+                              +------|            |
